title: Aruba Switch 6100 Series: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/aruba
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the temperature of Aruba 6100 devices.

 The device defines the thresholds for low and high temperature by itself.
 The default WARN thresholds are set to 5% below/above the device sensor's CRIT levels.
 When sensor is in 'fault' state, this check is in WARN state.

 The check uses the arubaWiredTempSensorEntry-MIB.

item:
 The sensor name.

discovery:
 One service is created for each temperature sensor.
